{
  "stem": "3988.2",
  "chunk_idx": 15,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, I would say that was under-- well, 1945.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "In the beginning of 1945.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Maybe January, you know, went and started going on the-- on the march.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Not a thing.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "No, we didn't know.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, we heard planes.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Yeah, we heard planes.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "In fact, if I'm not mistaken, a day before or two days before, the Russian planes came in and bombed Jaworzno.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You know, they bombed the German barracks.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, yeah.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They bombed the German barracks.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They missed us, you know.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They bombed the German barracks.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, yeah, yeah.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Well, they're talking.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You know, we know that hte Russian is coming in, you know.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, we said, well, maybe we'll be liberated.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You know, maybe we're free.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Maybe we'll be able to go home.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And then they-- next couple days, they start taking us on that march, you know.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, yeah.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They took us out.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we're marching.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I don't know how many days or how many nights.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I don't remember that.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But you know, I was getting weaker and weaker.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And on the march, when you went on a march, and somebody fell down, and he couldn't make it no more, he got tired, weak, you know, and everything, the last German in the column, you know, took out his pistol and, you know, gave you a bullet, you know, in the head, you know.",
      "word_count": 55
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And then we took the person, with-- moved them over to the side, you know, he shouldn't lay in the middle of the road and everything.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And I hardly could make it any more.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And it comes at night-- at night, we used to rest, and mostly on a farm.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And the farmer used to cook up-- you know, boil up a potato.",
      "word_count": 13
    }
  ],
